cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with deep learning and semantic segmentation of medical images, which are typically associated with computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of auto-context and multi-scale pyramid networks also suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. The dataset used in the paper is related to medical imaging, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the use of deep learning models for segmentation indicates the involvement of neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category.
